parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while in motion, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine seizes
stalls
or shuts down while driving
often with no warning lights or indicators. The vehicle may experience a loud knocking or clunking noise
and may be unable to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, causing the vehicle to stall or shut down while in motion.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive amounts of oil
often requiring frequent oil top-ups. The engine may experience a knocking or clunking noise
and may eventually seize or fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Seizure due to Manufacturing Defect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine seizure due to manufacturing defects can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while in motion, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine seizes or fails due to manufacturing defects
such as metal shavings or debris in the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake System Failure (ABS, Hydraulic) - Parts Distribution Disconnect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
ABS and other brake warning lights illuminate
vehicle independently accelerates
vehicle unintendedly rolls forward
brake fluid level is low
abnormal high-pitched motor sound
explosion and white smoke from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause difficulty when reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The camera stopped working
making it hard to see when backing up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle RPM shoots up and the engine revs up when accelerating from a stopped position
causing the vehicle to jerk forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Multiple Warning Lights and System Failures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of multiple safety systems, including ABS, ESC, DBC, and parking brake, can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Multiple warning lights
including ABS
ESC
DBC
and parking brake
come on simultaneously
indicating system failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine makes noises
followed by a popping sound
and the vehicle shuts off
with smoke coming out from under the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Remote Start and Safety Feature Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to transfer ownership of remote start and safety features can compromise safety and security.
symptoms: The original owner maintains remote control of door lock/unlock features
remote start
and stop functions
making it impossible for the new owner to access these features.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle to start or stall while driving can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle won't start
or stalls while driving
with the engine making loud tapping noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The sunroof spontaneously explodes
shattering glass and falling into the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the vehicle can cause electrical issues, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Water enters the vehicle through a seal above the dashboard
causing electrical issues and potentially leading to engine failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The seizure of the engine can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, and recall issues can compromise safety.
symptoms: The engine seizes
causing the vehicle to lose power
and the check engine warning light
battery light
and oil light come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Hood Latch Recall and Reimbursement Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The difficulty in getting a replacement part for the hood latch recall can compromise safety and cause frustration.
symptoms: The hood latch recall process is difficult
with long wait times and unresponsive reimbursement requests.
